elements.text:
Key Non Functional Reqs:
1. Delay in notification - 
    A few seconds acceptable.
2. Delayed notifications OK BUT
    SHOULD NOT BE DROPPED.
3. Avoid Double-sending
4. Upto 50 million total cards+accounts
5. ~15M unique users
6. Peak: ~20k txns per second
